This is a personal collection of documents and software that is hosted for
archival purposes and in the spirit of sharing knowledge. All material hosted
here is either in the Public Domain, copyleft, or considered abandonware.
Please contact me at <ben@oneill.sh> if you would like to make a
contribution or if you would like to request that something be removed.

Regarding software hosted here, this is not to be considered a mirror or an
up-to-date repository. Some of this stuff is very old and likely riddled
with security vulnerabilities. Nothing here is known to be intentionally
malicious, but proceed at your own risk.
